<p>A <b>futures exchange</b> is a central financial exchange where people can trade standardized <a href="/wiki/Futures_contracts" title="Futures contracts" class="mw-redirect">futures contracts</a>; that is, a contract to buy specific quantities of a <a href="/wiki/Commodity" title="Commodity">commodity</a> or <a href="/wiki/Financial_instrument" title="Financial instrument">financial instrument</a> at a specified price with <a href="/wiki/Delivery_(commerce)" title="Delivery (commerce)">delivery</a> set at a specified time in the future.</p>
